program: A246707(n) = { local(A); if( n<0, 0, A = x * O(x^n); polcoeff( eta(x + A)^2 * eta(x^2 + A) * eta(x^3 + A)^2 * eta(x^6 + A) / (eta(x^4 + A) * eta(x^12 + A)), n)); }; \\ From A246707
